content: odilitime: Focused on enhancing the plugin ecosystem, merging a significant PR in elizaos-plugins/plugin-solana#16 that introduced numerous improvements and type fixes (+744/-276 lines). They also began a refactor of plugin initialization in elizaos-plugins/plugin-birdeye#6 and provided several code reviews. This week's contributions were a mix of bug fixes and other enhancements, primarily modifying code and configuration files.
